gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 140, Wizards 112
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeated the Wizards, 140-112. Bradley Beal notched a season-high 43 points (4-5 3PM) along with six assists for the Suns, with Jusuf Nurkic adding 18 points, 13 rebounds, and eight assists in the victory. Deni Avdija tallied 24 points (3-5 3PM) and three rebounds for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Suns improve to 29-21, while the Wizards fall to 9-40.
